{
  "stem": "12674.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, in 19-- I believe it started either in late 1939 or 1940.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I unfortunately do not remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But every Jew had to wear a yellow star that is-- said Jude, Jew, in German letters, which were written like Hebrew characters, with the thickening on the crosspieces and-- and so on.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everybody had to wear it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] did not want to.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And being very stubborn and headstrong and very stupid and young at the time, decided I wasn't going to wear it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And it-- it-- it was a-- a crime punishable by death.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If-- if-- if-- if-- if some-- if they found somebody, the whole family was sent to-- to-- was sent away.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't know about concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I had no idea these places existed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were sent to Poland, and nobody was ever heard from again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we knew, but we thought they were just locking them up, or they were in jail.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We didn't know they were gassing them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We were not-- this-- this was not aware.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We were only-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] listening to foreign radio was punishable by death.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And everyday people, if they did, they didn't tell twelve-year-old children about it, because the mouth, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I never knew anything that went on, except what I-- what was available through the German propaganda machine.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, to get back to the star.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I decided I wasn't going to wear it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I really endangered my family, and I endangered everybody's life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I guess every once in a while something has to go right.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody ever caught me, because I never wore it.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
